title: BBQ Beef & Filo Pastry Pie with Sesame Seeds & Cheddar Cheese
description: Everyone will be stopping to smell the enticing scent of this barbecue spiced pie. Best of all it’s super easy to make. Cooking all
the veggies in a variety of seasonings, baking it with Cheddar cheese and topping it with scrunched filo pastry brings everything
together for the whole family to enjoy.

